{"tid":1161893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(巴打入)一個月打幾多次飛機？","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:15:33.000Z","uid":194656,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d438d216e9348ae24a5adef0dd3613d5bede3d8e","tid":1161893,"uid":194656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"絲問。同男朋友一齊左幾個月，頭先問佢一個月打幾多次飛機，佢話一個月一至兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢係我初戀，我唔清楚男仔通常打幾多次，但我覺得一個月得一、兩次真係有啲少，佢年紀又唔係大，都係20頭。我好認真對待呢段感情，我比得個處佢就係想同佢行到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但知道左佢打飛機次數後，就怕同佢之後嘅性生活會不協調。我自認性慾強，如果一個月搞一、兩次係滿足唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一個月打一、兩次飛機係正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75875842a093e5560c2790f06fda39a94d002b5f","tid":1161893,"uid":225878,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"你打幾多次"},{"pid":"40aeb4219da42890c5e14f3806e0ca84eb96b58d","tid":1161893,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"你問吓佢係咪對住你打飛機好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1628d6271f5b7788a3c65481b3ee94c8711afbf5","tid":1161893,"uid":132227,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"平均30次啦 計埋有啲日子太忙打唔到 但之後補番2q<br />\n同你講一兩次係怕醜扮正直架啫"},{"pid":"b360d71da1533e89fb1b42abeed0d72addf43e57","tid":1161893,"uid":203417,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"一日兩至三次"},{"pid":"3ae253bb3dad6b8f7f18bb20ba2406b72b44ba3b","tid":1161893,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"一日十次"},{"pid":"20a288955edc67c6f2235108e0576baf179eec7c","tid":1161893,"uid":119302,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"唔知你真膠定假膠，不過認真答你<br />\n我平均一